➜English Night｜Shut Out That Moon
http://www.sohu.com/a/434854021_404517	48888
<p style="text-align: center;"><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></strong><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">Shut Out That Moon</span></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px;">挡住那个月亮</span></strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>By Thomas Hardy</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><span>作者：托马斯·哈代</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Close up the casement, draw the blind,</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">闭上窗户，拉起窗帘，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Shut out that stealing moon,</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">挡住那悄悄熘来的月亮，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">She wears too much the guise she wore—</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">她的装束太像她以前——</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Before our lutes were strewn</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">当我们的诗琴还未积上</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">With years-deep dust, and names we read</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">岁月的尘埃，我们念到的名字</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">On a white stone were hewn.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">还未刻在石碑之上。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201128/f54f80a261ec4709838a858ce84ebc9e.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Step not forth on the dew-dashed lawn</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">莫要去踏沾了露水的草坪</span></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">To view the Lady’s Chair,</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">去观望仙后座的模样，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Immense Orion’s glittering form,</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">以及猎户座的闪烁的形象，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">The Less and Greater Bear;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">还有大熊座和小熊座；</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Stay in; to such sights we were drawn</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">闭门不出吧；我们曾被那番景色吸引</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">When faded ones were fair.</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">当美好的东西仍末凋亡。</span></p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201128/818d83ab9d8e4339a0f09586578d08c7.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Brush not the bough for midnight scents</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">切莫去拂除花丛，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">That come forth lingeringly,</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">让午夜的香气缠绵不逸，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">And wake the same sweet sentiments</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">唤醒那同样的甜蜜情意，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">They breathed to you and me</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">像当年向你我吹拂的那般</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">When living seemed a laugh, and love</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">那时节，生活就像在欢笑，</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">All it was said to be!</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">爱情美好得如人们的描述！</span></p>
<p><span>&gt;</span><span>&gt;</span><span>&gt;</span><span>&gt;</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>字词解析：</strong></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">casement </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">窗户</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">/ˈkeɪsmənt/</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">lute </span><span style="font-size: 16px;">诗琴</span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">/luːt/</span></p>
<p><strong>作者</strong><strong></strong></p>
<p><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/q_70/images03/20201128/369ee300dacd423ca6335e1cc1d3fe61.jpeg" /></p>
<p><span><span style="font-size: 16px;">托马斯·哈代，英国诗人、小说家。代表作有《</span><span style="font-size: 16px;">德伯家的苔丝》等。</span></span><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>
<p><strong>朗读者</strong></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">Angel Xie，国际学校英语教师，硕士毕业于英国伦敦大学学院（ <span style="font-size: 16px;">UCL</span>）语言学专业。 </span><span style="font-size: 16px;"></span></p>
